    • Field Detail

      • LOADED_DATA_RELATIVE_PATH

        public static final String LOADED_DATA_RELATIVE_PATH
        Deprecated. 
        Pointer to the path where the already loaded data should be written and retrieved. It is expressed relatively to the "cartagen" directory, which is the main directory of the application and can therefore be retrieved at runtime with System.getProperty("user.dir")
        See Also:
